com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common

Class StringReplaceBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.StringReplaceBundle

  • public class StringReplaceBundle
extends java.lang.Object
    Can perform a large amount of String replacements at once. The entries added may not contain null from or to.
